<strong>[<a href="/scp-3034">SCP-3034</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/WuSeQesaiXA">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-3034">The Counting Station</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>DO NOT LET HER FINISH</em>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;"> ►&nbsp;Commentary</a></div>
