<strong>[<a href="/scp-3117">SCP-3117</a>] [<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=td-_pUPVjdo">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-3117">A Monster-Shaped Hole</a></em></strong><br />
