<strong>[<a href="/scp-3219">SCP-3219</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/hfzrRdarnEs">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-3219">This Sour Earth</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>Notably, no reports describe any attempt to examine the residence's storm cellar.</em>
