<strong>[<a href="/scp-4054">SCP-4054</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/-sOadAaGiq4">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-4054">The Seventh Door</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>SCP-4054 is The Seventh Door, an unlicensed platform adventure game released for the Nintendo Entertainment System in 1988.</em>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;"> ►&nbsp;Commentary</a></div>
