<strong>[<a href="/scp-4153">SCP-4153</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/Dhfg8lRB-CQ">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-4153">Vincent Price Presents... IT CAME FROM SITE-9!</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em><strong>SUBJECT:</strong> Oh come now, Agent Penn. Have some respect for the classics.</em>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;"> ►&nbsp;Commentary</a></div>
