<strong>[<a href="/scp-4182">SCP-4182</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/5XZ_5B5mJS0">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-4182">There is no Site-5</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>see you there. ~:)</em>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;"> ►&nbsp;Commentary</a></div>
