<strong>[<a href="/scp-5141">SCP-5141</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/p8A5tfubT_k">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-5141">Studebaker Special Six</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>&quot;Son, you ever try to out-run a one-legged man in his own backyard?&quot;</em>
