<strong>[<a href="/scp-3352">SCP-3352</a>] [<a href="https://youtu.be/2yIELWjG8Tc">♬</a>] &#8212; <em><a href="/scp-3352">Bethlehem Steel</a></em></strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><em>For three minutes, the last thing — the only thing — standing between ten thousand souls and all the fires of hell was that thin solitary beam of Bethlehem steel.</em>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;"> ►&nbsp;Commentary</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
