<p>Written as part of the Doomcon contest (for team <a href="/k-o-failure-scenario-hub">JAWESOME</a>, which posited a doomsday event resulting from the SPC!) along with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721445" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span>. Not gonna lie, Peppersghost did the heavy lifting here; mostly I got this collab on account of making a lot of last minute edits (we posted it literally a minute before the deadline, with him writing out the journal and me coming up right behind him and rewriting it).</p>
